	'Timesheets' as Datamart,
	'Skill.Module.BusinessObjects.Timesheet' as DatamartDocumentType,
	FORMAT(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01), 'yyyy-MM-dd') as DatamartBeginDate,
	FORMAT(EOMONTH(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01)), 'yyyy-MM-dd') as DatamartEndDate,
	v.[Year], 
	v.[Month],
	FORMAT(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01), 'MMM', 'en-US') AS [MonthName], 
	SUM(v.OpCnt) AS OpCnt,
	SUM(v.DwCnt) AS DwCnt,
	(SUM(v.DwCnt) - SUM(v.OpCnt)) AS MissingDwCnt  
FROM
(
	SELECT 
		v.[Year], 
		v.[Month], 
		COUNT(*) as OpCnt,
		0 as DwCnt
	FROM 
		dbo.SkillTimesheet v
	GROUP BY 
		v.[Year], 
		v.[Month]
	UNION ALL
	SELECT 
		v.[Year], 
		v.[Month], 
		0 as OpCnt,
		COUNT(*) as DwCnt
	FROM 
		Analytics.DatamartTimesheet v
	GROUP BY 
		v.[Year], 
		v.[Month]
) v
GROUP BY
	v.[Year], 
	v.[Month]

UNION ALL

SELECT
	'Estimates' as Datamart,
	'Skill.Module.BusinessObjects.Estimate' as DatamartDocumentType,
	FORMAT(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01), 'yyyy-MM-dd') as DatamartBeginDate,
	FORMAT(EOMONTH(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01)), 'yyyy-MM-dd') as DatamartEndDate,
	v.[Year], 
	v.[Month],
	FORMAT(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01), 'MMM', 'en-US') AS [MonthName], 
	SUM(v.OpCnt) AS OpCnt,
	SUM(v.DwCnt) AS DwCnt,
	(SUM(v.DwCnt) - SUM(v.OpCnt)) AS MissingDwCnt  
FROM
(
	SELECT 
		Year(v.[Date]) AS [Year], 
		Month(v.[Date]) AS [Month], 
		COUNT(*) as OpCnt,
		0 as DwCnt
	FROM 
		dbo.Estimate v, 
		dbo.EstimateItem eit, 
		dbo.EstimateItemDetail edt
	WHERE
		eit.Estimate = v.Oid
		AND edt.EstimateItem = eit.Oid
	GROUP BY 
		Year(v.[Date]), 
		Month(v.[Date])
	UNION ALL
	SELECT 
		v.[Year], 
		v.[Month], 
		0 as OpCnt,
		COUNT(*) as DwCnt
	FROM 
		Analytics.DatamartEstimate v
	GROUP BY 
		v.[Year], 
		v.[Month]
) v
GROUP BY
	v.[Year], 
	v.[Month]
UNION ALL
SELECT

	'Skill.Module.BusinessObjects.Holiday' as DatamartDocumentType,
	FORMAT(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01), 'yyyy-MM-dd') as DatamartBeginDate,
	FORMAT(EOMONTH(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01)), 'yyyy-MM-dd') as DatamartEndDate,
	v.[Year], 
	v.[Month],
	FORMAT(DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 01), 'MMM', 'en-US') AS [MonthName], 
	SUM(v.OpCnt) AS OpCnt,
	SUM(v.DwCnt) AS DwCnt,
	(SUM(v.DwCnt) - SUM(v.OpCnt)) AS MissingDwCnt  
FROM
(

		Year(v.[Date]) AS [Year],

		COUNT(*) as OpCnt,

	GROUP BY

	UNION ALL
	SELECT

		v.[Month],

	GROUP BY

) v

	(SUM(v.DwCnt) - SUM(v.OpCnt)) AS MissingDwCnt  
FROM

	SELECT 
		Year(v.AgreedDateUtc) AS [Year],

	FROM 
		Analytics.DatamartJob v
	GROUP BY

) v
GROUP BY
	v.[Year], 
	v.[Month]
